commit.message:
Added current location and haversine

-Haversine calculates the distance between two longitudes and latitudes
-getMyLoc() returns your current longitude and latitude
-getPossiblePlaces returns places that are possible for you to visit
given maxFee and maxDist
-Edited getData to give a list of dictionaries instead of a list of
lists to ease the access of specific values

Testing New Calculation

Totally worth a try
